| SSH Brute Force Detection — T1110
| Triggers on 5+ failed SSH attempts from a single IP within 60 seconds

index=main sourcetype=linux_secure "Failed password"
| rex field=_raw "from (?P<src_ip>\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+)"
| bucket _time span=60s
| stats count by src_ip, _time
| where count > 5
| sort -count
